00:06:38.272 --> 00:06:42.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>brilhando ao sol que se punha,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>roxo como um dedo machucado."</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:06:42.485 --> 00:06:44.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O que é roxo? O nariz ou o sol?</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:06:44.445 --> 00:06:45.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não sei mais!</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:06:45.988 --> 00:06:48.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quem se importa com a reação do nariz?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Odeio isto!</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:06:50.493 --> 00:06:53.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Já pensou em escrever "contos de fodas"?</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:06:53.746 --> 00:06:57.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tanta escrita,</c.bg_transparent>
