111
00:06:57.625 --> 00:06:58.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Escreva uma peça.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:06:58.543 --> 00:07:00.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tipo um monólogo?</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:00.086 --> 00:07:02.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não, meu Deus! Quero ajudar sua carreira,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>não prejudicá-la.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:05.341 --> 00:07:09.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cai matando! Você tem dado tão duro</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que merece comer o sexto sonho.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:10.179 --> 00:07:13.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esta cena aqui é complicada.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:13.641 --> 00:07:15.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não sei bem como nós...</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:15.518 --> 00:07:16.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pai!</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:18.938 --> 00:07:20.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quando pediu a mão da mamãe...</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:21.357 --> 00:07:23.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por que estão arrancando as tulipas?</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:23.317 --> 00:07:25.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quero praticar arco e flecha.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:07:25.194 --> 00:07:28.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Queria um exercício</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>em que ficasse parado em pé.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:28.656 --> 00:07:29.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que ótimo.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:29.782 --> 00:07:34.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Você me contou como pediu a mão da mamãe.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não me lembro.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:07:35.204 --> 00:07:37.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ainda nem fiz a pergunta.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:07:37.165 --> 00:07:42.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>São águas passadas.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Não quero remexer nelas.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:07:46.591 --> 00:07:51.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas Dagmar fez parte das nossas vidas</c.bg_transparent>
