128
00:07:51.387 --> 00:07:53.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não podemos fingir que não aconteceu.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:07:53.598 --> 00:07:56.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sou rei! Faço o que bem quiser!</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:07:59.479 --> 00:08:02.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como se esconder no barracão até eu sair?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:02.857 --> 00:08:03.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Talvez.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:05.860 --> 00:08:08.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não preciso de ajuda.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Eu vivi essa história.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:08.863 --> 00:08:13.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É uma parte de mim e a tornarei real.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:15.036 --> 00:08:19.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Você me magoa, esposa.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Seu coração parece ser de gelo.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:19.457 --> 00:08:23.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tenho propósitos mais elevados</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>do que tuas preocupações mundanas.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:23.294 --> 00:08:25.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Não passas de um cavaleiro morto</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:25.963 --> 00:08:30.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>numa grande batalha</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>muito além da tua compreensão."</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:30.635 --> 00:08:34.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Quem cai em batalha só morre uma vez.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:34.722 --> 00:08:39.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ser traído pelo amor verdadeiro</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>é cem vezes pior."</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:08:39.810 --> 00:08:43.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"As cortinas se fecham, fim."</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:08:47.151 --> 00:08:51.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bravo! Uma obra comovente</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de um gênio médio a moderado.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:08:51.239 --> 00:08:53.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Foi um </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>tour de force</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> dramático.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:08:54.617 --> 00:08:57.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nunca me deixaram</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ficar tanto tempo sentada.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:08:58.663 --> 00:09:01.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eu estava esperando um suspense médico.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:01.457 --> 00:09:05.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obra fabulosa. De primeira classe.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Quer celebrar com um pequeno suicídio?</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:05.294 --> 00:09:07.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Não!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Só estou fazendo meu trabalho.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:07.129 --> 00:09:11.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Onde vai jogar seu roteiro?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Na lata de lixo, na casinha?</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:11.175 --> 00:09:13.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Devia ser representado no palco.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:13.761 --> 00:09:16.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É brilhante, mas o que sei eu?</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:16.514 --> 00:09:17.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não muito, na verdade.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:17.890 --> 00:09:19.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>TEATRO DA TERRA DOS SONHOS</c.bg_transparent>

152
