<c.bg_transparent>Oi. Será que posso oferecer minha peça...</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:30.945 --> 00:09:31.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:32.947 --> 00:09:34.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Posso marcar hora...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Não.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:35.700 --> 00:09:37.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Só queria saber se...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Não.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:39.829 --> 00:09:42.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Posso só entrar no teatro?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Não.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:43.082 --> 00:09:45.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por que todos</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:09:45.626 --> 00:09:48.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>podem entrar numa boa e eu não?</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:09:52.300 --> 00:09:54.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Não sabia?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-O quê?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:09:55.428 --> 00:09:57.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mulheres não podem trabalhar no teatro!</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:09:57.680 --> 00:10:00.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sei que se decepcionou, Bean,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mas o que esperava?</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:01.017 --> 00:10:03.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como ir à guerra</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e julgar concursos de miss,</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:03.352 --> 00:10:05.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>o teatro é um trabalho para homens.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:05.521 --> 00:10:09.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que ridículo. Não há motivos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para mulher não fazer teatro.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:09.358 --> 00:10:13.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>É uma coisa perigosa.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Depois vem o quê? Vacas machos?</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:14.238 --> 00:10:17.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eu mesmo já atuei na ribalta.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:18.534 --> 00:10:19.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ribalta?</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:19.702 --> 00:10:24.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Na Universidade da Cidade Cintilante,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>eu era o astro da folia anual.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:24.206 --> 00:10:26.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Meus fãs, estupefatos pelo meu talento,</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:26.500 --> 00:10:30.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>jogavam em mim tijolos caseiros</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e tomates maduros e frescos.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:31.172 --> 00:10:34.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Coisas do passado.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Minha época mais gloriosa.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:40.056 --> 00:10:44.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Olá. Sei que mulheres são proibidas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de trabalhar no teatro.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:44.143 --> 00:10:44.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sim.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:45.061 --> 00:10:46.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-E porcos?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Entre.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:46.854 --> 00:10:49.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Devo alertar:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lambuzei-me no próprio esterco.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:49.982 --> 00:10:51.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Já mandei entrar.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:10:55.196 --> 00:10:59.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Conseguiu que montassem minha peça?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Caramba, obrigada!</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:00.576 --> 00:11:04.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas há uma pequena condição.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Eles acham que sou o autor.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:04.955 --> 00:11:06.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quê? Como assim, "o autor"?</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:07.083 --> 00:11:10.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eu não podia contar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que foi escrita por uma mulher.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:10.169 --> 00:11:12.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>O crédito pode ser meu,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mas o pagamento é todo seu.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:14.340 --> 00:11:17.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vai me pagar comigo?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Não preciso de dinheiro.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:17.718 --> 00:11:22.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Escrevi para ficar em paz</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>com minha família e meu passado.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:22.473 --> 00:11:25.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me dediquei de corpo e alma.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Isso não tem preço.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:25.601 --> 00:11:28.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>É um insulto sugerir dinheiro.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Eu cuido disso, valeu.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:28.854 --> 00:11:33.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Felizmente, eles me deram</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>algo que vale mais que dinheiro.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:33.109 --> 00:11:34.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O papel de protagonista.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:34.527 --> 00:11:38.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vai me representar?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Meu personagem é a estrela da peça.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:38.614 --> 00:11:40.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tive de fazer ajustes.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:42.868 --> 00:11:43.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que tristeza...</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:45.663 --> 00:11:46.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Bean?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-O que foi?</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:11:46.789 --> 00:11:49.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tenho uma pergunta.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Não me jogue pela janela.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:11:49.125 --> 00:11:50.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isso não é pergunta.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:11:50.876 --> 00:11:53.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não me jogue pela janela?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Tenho outra pergunta.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:11:53.879 --> 00:11:56.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Posso ir ao teatro ser seu espiãozinho.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:11:56.424 --> 00:11:57.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Também não é pergunta.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:11:58.008 --> 00:12:00.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alguém pequeno será defenestrado.</c.bg_transparent>

